      &lt;img alt="iPhone 16" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-yGQzgoydv-I8AMcbWt0Hy5lVho=/0x0:2000x1333/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73582249/DSC08315_processed.0.jpg" /&gt;
